label: Submit Power Point Slides for Oral Presentation
quote: The Quoter shall submit the Power Point Slides for the Oral Presentation to the Contract Specialist with the proposal.

label: Submit pricing information using provided Pricing Schedule
quote: The pricing information shall be submitted using the Pricing Schedule provided in the solicitation.

label: Ensure template cells/formulas are visible and unlocked in pricing submission
quote: Please ensure that the template cells/formulas are visible and unlocked.

label: Submit pricing information correctly and by proposal due date
quote: The Contractor shall be responsible for ensuring that the pricing information is submitted correctly and submitted by the proposal due date.

label: Use labor rates in HCATS IDIQ Contract for pricing
quote: The Quoter shall use the labor rates in their HCATS IDIQ Contract

label: Quote labor categories and hours that best meet proposed solution
quote: Quoters shall be responsible for quoting the labor categories and hours that best meet the solution they are presenting.
